631
0:42:53,88 --> 0:42:57,12
A leaf is a chemical factory.


632
0:42:57,12 --> 0:43:0,92
It's a flat-roofed factory and
on the flat roof are solar panels


633
0:43:0,92 --> 0:43:5,72
