the machinery of the factory.


634
0:43:5,72 --> 0:43:9,84
There are wheels, almost literally
wheels going round and round,


635
0:43:9,84 --> 0:43:11,48
biochemical wheels,


636
0:43:11,48 --> 0:43:13,48
driven by the energy from the sun


637
0:43:13,48 --> 0:43:18,4
